{"tid":378534,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"識睇一定睇tvb舞王狄易達","createTime":"2017-08-28T14:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T11:01:35.000Z","uid":14730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a4d76dfe99c33b62f563d8dda959679ff9a9c5d2","tid":378534,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:34:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/223234_58cf1e4b92e4919314d3c1b3227e9744.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F223234_58cf1e4b92e4919314d3c1b3227e9744.jpg&h=ff27711e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTVB力捧的「舞王」狄易達，相信好多人記得他所主持的《安樂蝸》和他的break-dance。查實他身兼多職，做主持和歌手外，更是跳舞學校Dance Kingdom的導師（今年還開了一個裝修配對平台，當上老闆）。<br />\n<br />\n而狄易達跳舞名曲也不少，〈霹靂干戈〉和〈一天一粒糖〉和〈明日之謎〉是粉絲懂得跟著跳的舞曲。而值得尊重的是，他對歌唱事業的熱誠，令不少歌迷更期待他的演出！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2xqLk2T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2xqLk2T&d=GJF458Ascgpdq%2BHFbQ4yE9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=9bb4caaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2xqLk2T</a>"},{"pid":"63299f2dac46ef220123da44c4788b6b79b49084","tid":378534,"uid":3203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:37:23.000Z","msg":"係雅蘭床褥(狄易達)"},{"pid":"e89fe797065c0d600f5e36ddd480f6da8cccb1eb","tid":378534,"uid":19072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:17:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11bbc5b45e4a17e21e7ab4fa9e44c7bee621e4b9","tid":378534,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:29:27.000Z","msg":"咁真心佢啲歌係幾正<br />\nOne two three four 在我誕生的最初<br />\n基因已經吩咐我 在身體起舞麼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d569b319d263f750b6ed2b47e016ff7b2de2be","tid":378534,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T06:09:29.000Z","msg":"<a 